#: src/errormessages.js:22
msgid "No disk space left on server."
msgstr "Níl spás diosca fágtha ar an bhfreastalaí."

#: src/errormessages.js:23
msgid ""
"The host URL is empty. The coolwsd server is probably misconfigured, please "
"contact the administrator."
msgstr ""
"Tá URL an óstaigh folamh. Is dócha go bhfuil an freastalaí coolwsd "
"míchumraithe, déan teagmháil leis an riarthóir le do thoil."

#: src/errormessages.js:24
msgid ""
"This is an unsupported version of {productname}. To avoid the impression "
"that it is suitable for deployment in enterprises, this message appears "
"when more than {docs} documents or {connections} connections are in use "
"concurrently."
msgstr ""
"Seo leagan nach dtacaítear leis de {productname}. Chun an tuiscint go bhfuil "
"sé oiriúnach le himscaradh i bhfiontair a sheachaint, feictear an "
"teachtaireacht seo nuair a bhíonn níos mó ná doiciméid {docs} nó naisc "
"{naisc} in úsáid i gcomhthráth."

#: src/errormessages.js:25
msgid "More information and support"
msgstr "Tuilleadh eolais agus tacaíochta"

#: src/errormessages.js:26
msgid ""
"This service is limited to {0} documents, and {1} connections total by the "
"admin. This limit has been reached. Please try again later."
msgstr ""
"Tá an tseirbhís seo teoranta do {0} doiciméad, agus {1} nasc san iomlán ag "
"an riarthóir. Tá an teorainn seo sroichte. Bain triail eile as ar ball."

#: src/errormessages.js:27
msgid ""
"Service is unavailable. Please try again later and report to your "
"administrator if the issue persists."
msgstr ""
"Níl an tseirbhís ar fáil. Bain triail eile as ar ball agus cuir in iúl le do "
"riarthóir má leanann an fhadhb."

#: src/errormessages.js:28
msgid ""
"Unauthorized WOPI host. Please try again later and report to your "
"administrator if the issue persists."
msgstr ""
"Óstach WOPI neamhúdaraithe. Bain triail eile as ar ball agus cuir in iúl le "
"do riarthóir má leanann an fhadhb."

#: src/errormessages.js:29
msgid "Authorization error was: '{errormessage}'."
msgstr "Earráid údaraithe: '{errormessage}'."

#: src/errormessages.js:30
msgid "Wrong or missing WOPISrc parameter, please contact support."
msgstr ""
"Paraiméadar WOPISrc mícheart nó in easnamh, déan teagmháil leis an "
"bhfoireann tacaíochta."

#: src/errormessages.js:31
msgid ""
"Your session will expire in {time}. Please save your work and refresh the "
"session (or webpage) to continue. You might need to login again."
msgstr ""
"Rachaidh do sheisiún in éag i gceann {time}. Sábháil do chuid oibre agus "
"athnuaigh an seisiún (nó an leathanach gréasáin) chun leanúint ar aghaidh. "
"Seans go mbeidh ort logáil isteach arís."

#: src/errormessages.js:32
msgid ""
"Your session has expired. Further changes to the document might not be "
"saved. Please refresh the session (or webpage) to continue. You might need "
"to login again."
msgstr ""
"Tá do sheisiún imithe in éag. Seans nach sábhálfar a thuilleadh athruithe ar "
"an doiciméad. Athnuaigh an seisiún (nó an leathanach gréasáin) chun leanúint "
"ar aghaidh. Seans go mbeidh ort logáil isteach arís."

#: src/errormessages.js:33
msgid ""
"Failed to load the document. Please ensure the file type is supported and "
"not corrupted, and try again."
msgstr ""
"Theip ar lódáil an doiciméid. Cinntigh le do thoil go dtacaítear leis an "
"gcineál comhaid agus nach bhfuil sé truaillithe, agus bain triail eile as."

#: src/errormessages.js:34
msgid "Invalid link: '{url}'"
msgstr "Nasc neamhbhailí: '{url}'"

#: src/errormessages.js:35
msgid ""
"You are leaving the document. The following web page will open in a new "
"tab: "
msgstr ""
"Tá tú ag fágáil an doiciméid. Osclófar an leathanach gréasáin seo a leanas i "
"gcluaisín nua: "

#: src/errormessages.js:36
msgid ""
"Failed to load the document. This document is either malformed or is taking "
"more resources than allowed. Please contact the administrator."
msgstr ""
"Theip ar lódáil an doiciméid. Tá an doiciméad seo míchumtha nó tá níos mó "
"acmhainní á n-úsáid aige ná mar a cheadaítear. Déan teagmháil leis an "
"riarthóir le do thoil."

#: src/errormessages.js:37
msgid "Cleaning up the document from the last session."
msgstr "An doiciméad a ghlanadh ón seisiún deiridh."

#: src/errormessages.js:38
msgid ""
"We are in the process of cleaning up this document from the last session, "
"please try again later."
msgstr ""
"Táimid i mbun an doiciméad seo a ghlanadh ón seisiún deiridh, bain triail "
"eile as ar ball le do thoil."

#: src/errormessages.js:39
msgid ""
"Your {productname} cluster appear to be mis-configured or scaling rapidly - "
"please contact your system administrator. Continuing with editing may "
"result in multiple users not seeing each other, conflicts in the document "
"storage and/or copy/paste problems. Expected serverId {0} for routeToken "
"{1} but connected to serverId {2}"
msgstr ""
"Is cosúil go bhfuil do bhraisle {productname} míchumraithe nó go bhfuil sé "
"ag scála go tapa - déan teagmháil le riarthóir do chórais. Má leantar leis "
"an eagarthóireacht d’fhéadfadh sé tarlú nach bhfeiceann úsáideoirí iolracha "
"a chéile, go mbeadh coinbhleachtaí ann maidir le stóráil doiciméad agus/nó "
"fadhbanna cóipe/greamaigh. Bhíothas ag súil le serverId {0} le haghaidh "
"routeToken {1} ach nasctha le serverId {2}"

#: src/errormessages.js:40
msgid ""
"Failed to establish socket connection or socket connection closed "
"unexpectedly. The reverse proxy might be misconfigured, please contact the "
"administrator. For more info on proxy configuration please checkout https://"
"sdk.collaboraonline.com/docs/installation/Proxy_settings.html"
msgstr ""
"Theip ar bhunú nasc soicéad nó nasc soicéad dúnta gan choinne. Seans go "
"bhfuil an seachfhreastalaí cúil míchumraithe, déan teagmháil leis an "
"riarthóir le do thoil. Le haghaidh tuilleadh eolais ar chumraíocht "
